1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,949
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,950 --> 00:00:32,324
=Episode 10=
(The thought of parting from you again)

3
00:00:32,325 --> 00:00:34,870
(drives me mad with pain.)

4
00:01:00,780 --> 00:01:03,820
Since when did Rong Manor collude
with the Flower Slaves?

5
00:01:04,140 --> 00:01:06,499
Never learns, huh?

6
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:09,140
Immortal, leave the shadow guards to me.

7
00:01:09,460 --> 00:01:11,220
And I'll handle the Flower Slaves.

8
00:01:19,220 --> 00:01:20,380
Don't run!

9
00:01:31,260 --> 00:01:32,139
General,

10
00:01:32,140 --> 00:01:33,259
they're all under control.

11
00:01:33,260 --> 00:01:35,379
Take the Flower Slaves
and the shadow guards back.

12
00:01:35,380 --> 00:01:36,539
Detain them separately.

13
00:01:36,540 --> 00:01:37,819
See that nothing goes wrong.

14
00:01:37,820 --> 00:01:38,820
Yes, General.

15
00:01:42,140 --> 00:01:43,259
Miss, take a look.

16
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:44,860
My Lady, over here!

17
00:01:45,980 --> 00:01:48,499
My Lady, how about this one?

18
00:01:48,500 --> 00:01:49,860
This?

19
00:01:51,900 --> 00:01:53,300
He'll definitely like it.

20
00:01:54,060 --> 00:01:57,619
I bet he'll say,

21
00:01:57,620 --> 00:01:59,419
"I can't accept a reward I didn't earn,"

22
00:01:59,420 --> 00:02:02,380
"but I appreciate your thought."

23
00:02:04,420 --> 00:02:06,220
Isn't that just like him?

24
00:02:07,180 --> 00:02:08,580
By the way,

25
00:02:08,700 --> 00:02:11,139
how do you know him so well?

26
00:02:11,140 --> 00:02:12,339
I don't.

27
00:02:12,340 --> 00:02:14,220
It just feels like that's how he is.

28
00:02:16,180 --> 00:02:18,179
Maybe that's what they call

29
00:02:18,180 --> 00:02:19,660
love at first sight.

30
00:02:24,700 --> 00:02:25,860
Ten coins.

31
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,500
Thank you.

32
00:02:38,060 --> 00:02:38,699
Happy New Year.

33
00:02:38,700 --> 00:02:40,860
- Happy New Year to you too.
- It's so lively over there!

34
00:02:42,700 --> 00:02:44,140
Slow down.

35
00:02:47,380 --> 00:02:48,780
That dance is amazing.

36
00:02:49,020 --> 00:02:49,659
Make way.

37
00:02:49,660 --> 00:02:51,100
So festive.

38
00:02:54,180 --> 00:02:55,620
So lively.

39
00:02:56,100 --> 00:02:57,380
Yeah, look.

40
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:58,540
Nice.

41
00:02:59,220 --> 00:03:00,380
My Lady.

42
00:03:00,900 --> 00:03:02,059
Come join us.

43
00:03:02,060 --> 00:03:03,220
My Lady.

44
00:03:03,900 --> 00:03:05,260
This is fun!

45
00:03:07,340 --> 00:03:08,420
My Lady.

46
00:03:10,340 --> 00:03:11,411
Nice.

47
00:03:11,412 --> 00:03:12,452
My Lady?

48
00:03:14,060 --> 00:03:15,060
My Lady!

49
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:18,380
Make way.

50
00:03:19,060 --> 00:03:19,980
Move.

51
00:03:20,340 --> 00:03:21,019
Nice one.

52
00:03:21,020 --> 00:03:22,100
Move!

53
00:03:25,580 --> 00:03:26,500
My Lady!

54
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:28,660
My Lady!

55
00:03:30,940 --> 00:03:32,100
My Lady!

56
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:37,060
(Master, Miss Xihe is gone!)

57
00:03:39,340 --> 00:03:40,660
Xi is missing?

58
00:03:41,060 --> 00:03:42,180
It's a diversion.

59
00:03:42,340 --> 00:03:42,779
Weiguo.

60
00:03:42,780 --> 00:03:43,179
Yes?

61
00:03:43,180 --> 00:03:44,899
- Mobilize the troops now.
- Yes!

62
00:03:44,900 --> 00:03:46,500
Move!

63
00:03:47,780 --> 00:03:48,420
Quick!

64
00:03:59,900 --> 00:04:00,779
(You again?)

65
00:04:00,780 --> 00:04:03,339
(How long will you toy with me and her?)

66
00:04:03,340 --> 00:04:05,540
(Return her at once!)

67
00:04:07,580 --> 00:04:10,859
Blaming everything on fate
when things go wrong.

68
00:04:10,860 --> 00:04:12,260
How childish.

69
00:04:12,660 --> 00:04:14,019
Everything today

70
00:04:14,020 --> 00:04:15,939
is your own doing.

71
00:04:15,940 --> 00:04:17,620
What does it have to do with me?

72
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:23,700
(Xi, where are you?)

73
00:04:27,300 --> 00:04:28,580
Xi!

74
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:31,140
Xi!

75
00:04:48,260 --> 00:04:49,540
You look

76
00:04:49,860 --> 00:04:51,220
so much like her.

77
00:04:54,140 --> 00:04:56,340
But you can't be her.

78
00:04:56,780 --> 00:05:00,540
I buried Xihe with my own hands
100 years ago.

79
00:05:04,780 --> 00:05:06,139
Who are you?

80
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:07,459
How dare you abduct me?

81
00:05:07,460 --> 00:05:08,979
Your Highness,

82
00:05:08,980 --> 00:05:10,340
don't you remember?

83
00:05:10,580 --> 00:05:12,340
I told you,

84
00:05:13,220 --> 00:05:15,020
we mean no harm.

85
00:05:18,260 --> 00:05:20,260
It's you!

86
00:05:22,140 --> 00:05:24,580
Why did you capture me?

87
00:05:24,700 --> 00:05:27,139
I only wish to borrow something

88
00:05:27,140 --> 00:05:28,580
from you.

89
00:05:28,820 --> 00:05:29,819
What's that?

90
00:05:29,820 --> 00:05:30,940
Your life.

91
00:05:38,820 --> 00:05:40,579
Sacrifice her.

92
00:05:40,580 --> 00:05:42,140
Complete the ritual,

93
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:45,579
and our clan's century-long curse
will be broken.

94
00:05:45,580 --> 00:05:48,700
No more bone-piercing agony.

95
00:05:59,700 --> 00:06:00,780
The jade whistle.

96
00:06:30,900 --> 00:06:32,700
Zhang Muzhi!

97
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:34,900
You

98
00:06:35,340 --> 00:06:37,380
will die today!

99
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:39,019
Hold him back!

100
00:06:39,020 --> 00:06:41,380
The formation is nearly complete.
Don't ruin it!

101
00:06:43,340 --> 00:06:45,260
You think you can stop me?

102
00:07:02,060 --> 00:07:04,380
The Seer was right.

103
00:07:04,580 --> 00:07:07,340
I mixed mortals among my people,

104
00:07:07,380 --> 00:07:09,219
triggering heavenly backlash on you.

105
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:11,699
Just now, I lied
about the formation being complete

106
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:13,940
to make you panic and lose control.

107
00:07:15,340 --> 00:07:16,580
Fool.

108
00:07:17,700 --> 00:07:20,460
If Xihe had chosen me back then,

109
00:07:20,500 --> 00:07:23,020
none of this would have happened.

110
00:07:32,060 --> 00:07:33,139
Brilliant plan, Immortal.

111
00:07:33,140 --> 00:07:34,259
Once this is done,

112
00:07:34,260 --> 00:07:36,900
don't forget my reward of immortality.

113
00:07:38,380 --> 00:07:39,580
Today,

114
00:07:39,820 --> 00:07:42,340
even if my divine heart is shattered,

115
00:07:43,260 --> 00:07:45,940
I will protect her.

116
00:08:03,762 --> 00:08:08,400
♪When starlight cuts
through the long night♪

117
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:16,320
♪it bids farewell to another blue sky♪

118
00:08:17,225 --> 00:08:19,411
♪To meet is to overlap♪

119
00:08:19,412 --> 00:08:21,349
♪To see is to part again♪

120
00:08:21,350 --> 00:08:24,679
♪To stay is to wish for forever♪

121
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:31,280
♪Counting every moment,
unwilling to pause♪

122
00:09:03,060 --> 00:09:04,380
Everyone, form the array!

123
00:09:06,700 --> 00:09:08,940
Helian Shu, what are you waiting for?

124
00:09:25,262 --> 00:09:32,361
♪I never got the chance
to tell you how I felt♪

125
00:09:32,362 --> 00:09:36,680
♪If the rain never stops, the wind
never fades, and time stands still♪

126
00:09:36,750 --> 00:09:39,990
♪Let this love go on♪

127
00:09:50,875 --> 00:09:52,584
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

128
00:09:52,585 --> 00:09:55,434
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

129
00:09:55,435 --> 00:09:58,174
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

130
00:09:58,175 --> 00:09:59,804
♪Let the long shadows♪

131
00:09:59,805 --> 00:10:05,405
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

132
00:10:05,455 --> 00:10:07,054
♪If in a dream♪

133
00:10:07,055 --> 00:10:09,814
♪I can hear your voice♪

134
00:10:09,815 --> 00:10:12,664
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

135
00:10:12,665 --> 00:10:15,264
♪Let it be us♪

136
00:10:15,265 --> 00:10:20,054
♪drawing endlessly close♪

137
00:10:20,055 --> 00:10:21,814
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

138
00:10:21,815 --> 00:10:24,465
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

139
00:10:24,685 --> 00:10:27,404
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

140
00:10:27,405 --> 00:10:29,054
♪Not even in time♪

141
00:10:29,055 --> 00:10:34,714
♪to tell you how I feel♪

142
00:10:34,715 --> 00:10:36,254
♪If the rain won't stop♪

143
00:10:36,255 --> 00:10:39,004
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

144
00:10:39,005 --> 00:10:41,974
♪Let love go on♪

145
00:10:41,975 --> 00:10:44,524
♪Until forever♪

146
00:10:44,525 --> 00:10:49,164
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

147
00:10:49,165 --> 00:10:51,774
♪Until forever♪

148
00:10:51,775 --> 00:10:58,885
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
